column9:
What's Included
•	Entrance fees to attractions
•	Checkpoint formalities (e.g. border fees)

What's Not Included
•	Lunch
•	Personal expenses
•	Optional activity costs

What to Remember
You will need to present your passport during the U.N. border crossing.
Please bring or wear clothing appropriate for visiting churches and monasteries.

Please notify if you would like to have yoga matt provided for you. Don't forget to put on comfortable clothes, something you can move around easily with. Be prepared for your feet to get dirty or wet. You will also need a towel and a spare clean tshirt.

Cancellation Policy
All sales are final and incur 100% cancellation penalties.

Cancellation Policy
No fee for cancellations before 7+ days of the scheduled departure.
50% charge for cancellations within 3-6 days of the scheduled departure.
Full 100% charge for cancellations within 2 days of the scheduled departure.

Cancellation Policy

If you cancel at least 7 day(s) in advance of the scheduled departure, there is no cancellation fee.
If you cancel between 3 and 6 day(s) in advance of the scheduled departure, there is a 50 percent cancellation fee.
If you cancel within 2 day(s) of the scheduled departure, there is a 100 percent cancellation fee.
